<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5119670>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–5. 1. Pachyrhinus squamulosus, dorsal view. 2. Pachyrhinus head, lateral view. 3. Pachyrhinus tarsus showing connate tarsal claws. 4. Pachyrhinus head, frontal view. 5. Polydrusus sericeus (Schaller) head, frontal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5119670/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5119672>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6–9. Elytral Scales. 6. Pachyrhinus elegans. 7. Pachyrhinus californicus. 8. Pachyrhinus cinereus scale. 9. Polydrusus impressifrons Gyllenhall 1834." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5119672/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5119674>
    dc:description "FIGURES 10–15. Elytral Vestiture. 10. Pachyrhinus elegans. 11. Pachyrhinus californicus. 12. Pachyrhinus cinereus. 13. Pachyrhinus squamulosus. 14. Pachyrhinus lethierryi. 15. Polydrusus sericeus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5119674/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5119676>
    dc:description "FIGURES 16–19. 16. Mandibles showing scars at deciduous process attachment point. 17. Mandibles with deciduous process. 18. Oral cavity with maxillae and labium. 19. Antennae, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5119676/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5119678>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20–21. 20. Scutellum. 21. Male protibia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5119678/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5119682>
    dc:description "FIGURES 26–28. 26. Abdominal ventrites. 27. Spiculum gastrale. 28. Tegmen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5119682/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5119680>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22–25. 22. Elytra. 23. Puncture in elytral interstria. 24. Scales on elytral stria. 25. Wing." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5119680/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5119684>
    dc:description "FIGURES 29–32. 29. Female protibia. 30. Female abdominal ventrites. 31. Eighth sternite. 32. Ovipositor." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5119684/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

